title: Ep 130 - Frank Caliendo & More
description:
The boys spent the first 30 minutes speaking with legendary comedian and impressionist Frank Caliendo. They spent the rest of the episode talking about the usual stuff: Eccentric millionaires in New Zealand, sex tapes and embarrassing work stories.

For more from Frank Caliendo, check out his podcast The Frank Caliendo Cast and his comedy calendar at FrankCaliendo.com.
